kgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6c60843be0dc7faeaf2e987b5c2e6ed996fd56","tid":431404,"uid":44875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T16:00:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我2年前上堂識左個內向嘅女仔，嗰時同佢冇咩交流。直到上個月我WhatsApp搵返佢，我秒回佢，佢日回我，好似好被動噤。有時佢心情好會秒回，心情唔好會隔日回。 直至最近我想約佢食lunch俾佢藍剔左我，我傷心之下打左一大段野自爆。我仲有冇可能同佢做翻朋友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申： 佢唔玩fb、ig 又好少玩whatsapp 啲人黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會唔會淨係對你先內向？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都唔係 佢本身份人係超級內向<br />\n反而WhatsApp 會好認真覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f07937e34f47075ca83636e5f7c0b8c9dae564","tid":431404,"uid":127216,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T16:03:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>收手啦巴打<br />\n唔好丟架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我到依家都冇搵過佢<br />\n我以為自己學識灑脫<br />\n原來我只係一直抑壓自己感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁咪再搵下佢囉<br />\n點解要抑壓感情 辛苦既只會係自己<br />\n鐘意咪努力去爭取囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至少唔會令自己後悔呀<br />\n好難先可以搵到一個自己鐘意既人架"},{"pid":"ba9743ea82a2f314638474d0a6113d940aecc606","tid":431404,"uid":71581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T16:03:26.000Z","msg":"巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />夠鐘收皮啦<br />\n人地都做到咁明顯你仲嫌未柒夠"},{"pid":"c19f027b3d85e029cd454d5607194cd45c452dcc","tid":431404,"uid":44875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T16:04:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你自爆咗咩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n暗示我鍾意佢 <br />\n嗰晚醉左唔小心send 左出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲人會因為你講左一句我愛你，就成為你生命中嘅過客，你唔會再見到佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeccfc14fe09113c14f66d43c6ee43af68c3b35c","tid":431404,"uid":127216,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T16:06:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我2年前上堂識左個內向嘅女仔，嗰時同佢冇咩交流。直到上個月我WhatsApp搵返佢，我秒回佢，佢日回我，好似好被動噤。有時佢心情好會秒回，心情唔好會隔日回。 直至最近我想約佢食lunch俾佢藍剔左我，我傷心之下打左一大段野自爆。我仲有冇可能同佢做翻朋友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申： 佢唔玩fb、ig 又好少玩whatsapp 啲人黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會唔會淨係對你先內向？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都唔係 佢本身份人係超級內向<br />\n反而WhatsApp 會好認真覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係個超級內向既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但如果會認真覆 應該代表佢對你感覺okay既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至少冇反感"},{"pid":"19f46ada92d929717436f3f26085660f60d0fce6","tid":431404,"uid":44875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T16:06:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />夠鐘收皮啦<br />\n人地都做到咁明顯你仲嫌未柒夠</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唯一做到嘅就係上黎發洩，唔再搵佢，唔再係佢面前柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0570559e02817f947853b981adc98baea5fb9855","tid":431404,"uid":147445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T16:07:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>人地唔想理你<br />\n<br />\nOK?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOk 其實我知<br />\n只係得不到嘅友情同愛情都令人心悸<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n難捨難離</blockquote><br />\n依個時段<br />\n無論你做咩都好<br />\n係佢眼中只會令佢反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n就算你同另一個人做對佢做同一件事<br />\n佢都只會覺得你討厭,而唔會係討厭另外果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n停止交流一段時間先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d59856213a2bdb619e0fd250eb317752bf4cdea","tid":431404,"uid":44875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T16:11:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>收手啦巴打<br />\n唔好丟架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我到依家都冇搵過佢<br />\n我以為自己學識灑脫<br />\n原來我只係一直抑壓自己感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁咪再搵下佢囉<br />\n點解要抑壓感情 辛苦既只會係自己<br />\n鐘意咪努力去爭取囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至少唔會令自己後悔呀<br />\n好難先可以搵到一個自己鐘意既人架</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有時我對一個人嘅愛係唔可以比佢知道，因為太強烈、太恐怖，如果佢知道有人會無條件咁愛佢實會以為我係痴線佬。 我每次愛上一個都要抑壓自己嘅愛，唔可以比對方知，直至有一日呢份隨住時而消逝<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我只愛上過兩個女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56e6b6cbfd8a88447b4b454466c618489089ee24","tid":431404,"uid":44875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T16:13:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我2年前上堂識左個內向嘅女仔，嗰時同佢冇咩交流。直到上個月我WhatsApp搵返佢，我秒回佢，佢日回我，好似好被動噤。有時佢心情好會秒回，心情唔好會隔日回。 直至最近我想約佢食lunch俾佢藍剔左我，我傷心之下打左一大段野自爆。我仲有冇可能同佢做翻朋友？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申： 佢唔玩fb、ig 又好少玩whatsapp 啲人黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n會唔會淨係對你先內向？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n都唔係 佢本身份人係超級內向<br />\n反而WhatsApp 會好認真覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都係個超級內向既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但如果會認真覆 應該代表佢對你感覺okay既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n至少冇反感</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nHaha 曾經可能係 直至有一日佢開始突然醒覺我隱藏嘅愛意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我只係想了解你啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84974647532938c2128fcc63728f545854569fd0","tid":431404,"uid":44875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime